<plot>A young professional killer from the former Soviet Union, Aliosha, is assigned to perform a hit in Athens. He comes to Greece to kill Lampros but is accidentally arrested at a police roadblock. A Greek singer from Russia, Elena, searches for her lost son. Although she saw Aliosha the moment he was stepping out of Lampros' office, when called to identify him she covers for him with her silence. Aliosha's patrons, afraid of being exposed, decide to eliminate him, while the police are constantly watching him, since the head of the investigation never believed in his innocence.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?030260</url></doc>
